descriptionHtml:
Adds a book with a spell called Dark Times, the spell is basicly A Fus Ro Dah spell!
========================================================================================
The book is called \"in the dark times...\"  and can be found in Whiterun in Dragonreach (The big castle in Whiterun!)
========================================================================================
The spell does, like the Fus Ro Dah shout, not much damage - abit only- and does do the exact same
things like the Fus Ro Dah shout, EXTREME BLOWING WITH UR NORD MASTERED VOICE, EEGH I MEAN SPELL NOW!
========================================================================================
If there are any problems, feel free to report them to me.
========================================================================================
How to install:

Download the .esp and place it in your data folder....
